overview: August 2nd is time for the next GCW event! GCW "Keep in touch" features more than 6 matches with GCW fans favourite stars! Ace Austin and Kylie Rae will make their GCW in-ring debut, the opponents are TBA!  Already announced are:  Tony Deppen vs Benjamin Carter  Joey Janela vs ACH  Chris Dickinson vs AJ Gray  Calvin Tankman vs KTB  Christian Blake vs Tre Lamar  Mance Warner vs Nate Webb  44OH vs Effy w Allie Kat
title: GCW: Keep In Touch
